node.text:
[Singapore] 𝐓𝐔𝐊 𝐓𝐔𝐊 𝐂𝐇𝐀 ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
@tuktukcha has launched their Ramadan Sets! They come with mains and beverages such as my all-time fav iced thai green milk tea! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
• 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐇𝐚𝐩𝐩𝐢𝐧𝐞𝐬𝐬 𝐌𝐞𝐚𝐥 ($𝟐𝟗.𝟗𝟎)⁣⁣
4 mains and 4 beverages! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
• 𝐓𝐡𝐞 𝐀𝐛𝐮𝐧𝐝𝐚𝐧𝐜𝐞 𝐌𝐞𝐚𝐥 ($𝟓𝟗.𝟗𝟎)⁣⁣
6 mains, 6 beverages and 3 Golden Toasts! ⁣
⁣
Mains include items like:⁣
• Beef Noodles⁣
• Tom Yum Noodles ⁣
• Garlic Chicken Rice Bowl⁣
⁣
While the Ramadan sets are exclusively available for self pick-up/takeaway only, you'll be glad to know that they are having a 𝟸𝟶% 𝘥𝘪𝘴𝘤𝘰𝘶𝘯𝘵 𝘰𝘯 𝘥𝘦𝘭𝘪𝘷𝘦𝘳𝘺 𝘱𝘭𝘢𝘵𝘧𝘰𝘳𝘮𝘴 𝘴𝘶𝘤𝘩 𝘢𝘴 @𝘨𝘳𝘢𝘣𝘧𝘰𝘰𝘥𝘴𝘨 𝘢𝘯𝘥 @𝘧𝘰𝘰𝘥𝘱𝘢𝘯𝘥𝘢𝘴𝘨 𝘶𝘯𝘵𝘪𝘭 𝘊𝘉 𝘦𝘯𝘥𝘴! ⁣⁣
⁣⁣
Thai Milk Tea always makes me feel like I'm in Bangkok! With the super hot weather recently, iced cold thai milk tea really hit the spot! #tuktukchasg
I miss TTC’s Thai Milk Tea.
